    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirls, protected by a high-grade professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and exceptionally low mileage. From the factory-clean engine bay to the untouched door seals, every inch of this car has been meticulously detailed. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that feels, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
